<P>
PREP SOFTBALL '94 / SIX TEAMS TO WATCH; LOS ALAMITOS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Coach: Jami Shannon (16th year, 223-130-2). 
</P>
<P>
 1993: 24-4, 8-2 in the Empire League; lost to No. 1 Simi Valley, 1-0, in the 
Division I final. 
</P>
<P>
 Key returners: Megan Barnes, So., third baseman; Sheri Bergeron, Sr., P/1B; 
Amanda Peterson, Jr., second baseman/center fielder; Michelle Schneider, Jr., 
shortstop; Carolyn Wilson, Sr., catcher; Debora Wilson, Sr., pitcher/first 
