</P>
<P>
 Dolson, Eugene, 74, of Moorpark, retired Los Angeles police officer. 
Utter-McKinley Mortuary, Mission Hills. 
</P>
<P>
 Loughboro, Catherine, 88, of Ojai, chef. Ted Mayr Funeral Home, Ventura. 
</P>
<P>
 Ventura County obituaries are published free of charge as a public service to 
readers. Obituaries are based on information provided by mortuaries. 
