<P>
BOMB HOAX SNARLS TRAFFIC OVER POTOMAC 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A man claiming to have a bomb held police at bay for several hours Monday on a 
Potomac River bridge, snarling morning traffic in the nation's capital and 
disrupting Amtrak service along the East Coast. 
</P>
<P>
 Sadiq Abubakar drove his car into a barrier on the bridge and refused to let 
