<P>
 Kmart Shakes Up Bookstore Operations: In an effort to lure affluent younger 
readers, Kmart Corp. said it will close 187 of its 1,216 Waldenbook stores and 
upgrade its Borders super stores to a popular book and music format. The new 
format will combine books and music in a casual setting with novelties such as 
coffee bars and children's reading centers.The move comes as Kmart is putting 
