Borders-Waldenbooks to raise cash for its core discount store operation. Troy, 
Mich.-based Kmart acquired Borders in 1992 to strengthen its role as the 
nation's largest book retailer and compete with the growing popularity of 
Barnes & Noble's super stores. 
