<P>
REGIONAL EARNINGS: 4TH-QUARTER PROFIT UP AT WELLPOINT HEALTH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 WellPoint Health Networks Inc., a Woodland Hills managed health-care company, 
reported that its fourth quarter net income jumped 58% to $50.6 million. 
</P>
<P>
 A year earlier, WellPoint earned $32 million. Its quarterly revenue for the 
period ending Dec. 31 rose 10%, to $629.1 million from $571.5 million a year 
earlier. 
</P>
<P>
 For all of 1993, however, WellPoint's profit fell 5%, to $165.4 million from 
$174.8 million in 1992. Last year, its annual revenue totaled $2.45 billion, up 
8% from $2.28 billion in revenue in the previous year. 
</P>
