relations. Shufro, Rose now owns 446,327 shares of Wynn's common stock, valued 
at $9.9 million as of Monday's closing price of $22.25 a share. Wynn's 
manufactures automotive additives, air conditioning equipment, sealants and 
builders' hardware. 
