<HEADLINE>
<P>
GLOBOCARS: THE NEXT CENTURY; THE STAFF FOR 'GLOBOCARS' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 SECTION EDITOR: Nick B. Williams Jr. 
</P>
<P>
 NEWS EDITOR: Jane Engle 
</P>
<P>
 ART DIRECTOR: Matt Moody 
</P>
<P>
 ARTIST: James Owens 
</P>
