 CONTRIBUTORS: Mark Fineman, William Tuohy, William D. Montalbano, and Scott 
Kraft. 
</P>
<P>
 RESEARCHERS: Ann Griffith, Mary Edwards, Janet Lundblad and William Holmes in 
Los Angeles; Sarah White, Paris; Dianna Cahn, Jerusalem; Steve Gutterman, 
Moscow, and Christian Retzlaff, Berlin. 
</P>
