<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 1, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
World Report; Page 3; Column 1; World Report 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
